<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Be informed that Maiar have no names until they stray from their destined path...And such have they.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
