<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Morgoth stayed as the invisible hand of evil. Sauron himself took a form, many forms.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
